---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Endpoint Security | Paul Technologies">
  <Header />

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Endpoint Security & Hardening</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
      Endpoints remain the most common entry point for attackers. Poor defaults,
      misconfigurations, and lack of monitoring create unnecessary risk.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Our Focus</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-400 mb-8">
      <li>System hardening (Windows & Linux)</li>
      <li>EDR deployment and tuning</li>
      <li>Persistence & attack surface reduction</li>
      <li>Security baseline enforcement</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Frameworks</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
      CIS Benchmarks, MITRE ATT&CK, and real-world incident data guide our approach.
    </p>

    <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-primary text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-md">
      Secure Your Endpoints
    </a>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
